<p>This special page redirects to a file (given the filename), a page (given a revision ID or page ID), a user page (given a numeric user ID), or a log entry (given the log ID). Usage: <a href="/w/Special:Redirect/file/Example.jpg" title="Special:Redirect/file/Example.jpg">Special:Redirect/file/Example.jpg</a>, <a href="/w/Special:Redirect/page/64308" title="Special:Redirect/page/64308">Special:Redirect/page/64308</a>, <a href="/w/Special:Redirect/revision/328429" title="Special:Redirect/revision/328429">Special:Redirect/revision/328429</a>, <a href="/w/Special:Redirect/user/101" title="Special:Redirect/user/101">Special:Redirect/user/101</a>, or <a href="/w/Special:Redirect/logid/186" title="Special:Redirect/logid/186">Special:Redirect/logid/186</a>.
